title: Thrive
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Organic, Raw, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Serving raw and vegan food that's dairy free, gluten free, and peanut free. Menu is mostly all raw food, plus smoothies, fresh juices, warm grain bowls, and raw desserts. Mon-Thur full menu and cafe seating til 2:30pm and Sun til 4pm, then it's grab-n-go packaged dinners til closing. Fri-Sat full menu and seating all day. Also sells books and groceries.
